{"tid":1083877,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2020年是最後一次民主選舉？　《華盛頓郵報》：台灣變香港","createTime":"2019-03-30T03:17:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-30T04:30:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"dff60d9245b2e9876a8c235bc3748c62a35dc460","tid":1083877,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:17:46.000Z","msg":"海峽兩岸近年的互動逐漸升溫，尤其高雄市長韓國瑜拜訪中國大陸駐港最高機關中聯辦引發熱議。長期關注兩岸事務的《華盛頓郵報》專欄作家羅金（Josh Rogin）則撰文指出，在台灣內部隨處可見北京影響的痕跡，他認為美國應該要有所作為，正視台灣所面臨的民主危機，「否則2020年可能是台灣最後一次有意義的選舉。」<br />\n<br />\n羅金認為，中國國家主席習近平在《告台灣同胞書》發表40週年紀念會就明確表示，「一國兩制」在台灣的具體實現形式，等同試圖打破兩岸現狀。羅金在報導中引述陸委會副主委陳明祺的話，如果國民黨重新掌權，2020年以後的台灣選舉將轉為香港模式，「2020年可能是台灣最後一次有意義的選舉，2020年將是統一的開始。」<br />\n<br />\n    &ldquo;Washington must wake up to the danger of China&rsquo;s massive effort to infiltrate, undermine and eventually abolish Taiwan&rsquo;s democracy.&rdquo; <a href=\"https://t.co/e5rgUxZgKO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fe5rgUxZgKO&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7d%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=689d15a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/e5rgUxZgKO</a> My report from Taipei @PostOpinions<br />\n    &mdash; Josh Rogin (@joshrogin) 2019年3月29日<br />\n<br />\n羅金以「美國須幫助台灣抵抗中國統治」（The United States must help Taiwan resist Chinese dominance）為題，呼籲華府需意識到中國大陸不斷滲透並破壞台灣民主。羅金認為，儘管「台灣關係法」明確指出，「任何企圖以非和平方式來決定台灣的前途之舉，將被視為對西太平洋地區和平及安定的威脅，而為美國所嚴重關切。」但自2019年開始，北京當局卻無視這些文字，接連透過經濟、政治手段干涉台灣事務。<br />\n<br />\n北京對台灣的影響並不直接「硬著來」，羅金表示，他們透過親北京團體，大量收購台灣媒體，並在社群媒體中發散議題，更利用經濟、外交手段持續打壓台灣在國際組織內的地位。羅金甚至以高雄市長韓國瑜與中聯辦會晤舉例，他認為國民黨優先考慮哪一方顯而易見。<br />\n<br />\n儘管華府有許多親台官員，也非常有意願協助台灣捍衛民主，但數量與立場卻不夠穩定，美國也沒有完整的戰略可以應付中國大陸對台灣的威脅，但羅金認為台灣時間已經不多，美國政府應盡速有所作為。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190330/1411388.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190330%2F1411388.htm&d=tn6C2tKLXSv13zRFu6un7d%2FsvSzfkBtT%2Fd%2Bxj92WHuQ%3D&h=c2664c2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190330/1411388.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4cbe184c91002da2b06a6c34de6c91adc34e40a3","tid":1083877,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"黃毓民出聲屌《華盛頓郵報》無資格講台灣未？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53d1081451f8c00da896ac6a4f06942665229468","tid":1083877,"uid":6799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"發大財消滅民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca3391a2b574120d687ebebfd5ac0a4756ff10e7","tid":1083877,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53d1081451f8c00da896ac6a4f06942665229468","tid":1083877,"uid":6799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:38:11.000Z","msg":"發大財消滅民主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:45:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e38af1ff6beb2891cdfe9e07316b6485018ea65a","tid":1083877,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"2020年某度要亡國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306338722cee45ba92ce5a4c7ee241009d2e6d42","tid":1083877,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:46:29.000Z","msg":"香港模式選舉 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede39b556a311b3eca7a9e324a7079a58b2a189a","tid":1083877,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e38af1ff6beb2891cdfe9e07316b6485018ea65a","tid":1083877,"uid":25858,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"2020年某度要亡國了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-30T03:47:06.000Z","msg":"香港就係一國兩制最佳示範呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmo